      "content": "i'm just a bit worried about the cost of the clinic right now. i read online that medical grade honey is actually used in hospitals for wound healing because of its antibacterial stuff. won't that work just as well for a cut like this? i really dont want to make a huge deal out of it if i can just fix it here.",
