      "content": "i hear you but honestly the bleeding is slowing down a bit now that i've been holding it. it's not like it's spraying or anything, just soaking through the gauze every few mins. if i just clean it really well with some alcohol, put a thick layer of that honey on, and wrap it tight, can't i just monitor it at home? i really feel like i can handle this myself if i'm careful.",
